{
  "title": "Tapautaletalekane ki Ngudradrekay",
  "titleCh": "魯凱族的農業耕作",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "魯凱族善於種植農作物，用以料理、饗宴，在家裡享用許多名品食材與料理，在原住民社會是出了名的「吃的故鄉」。他們依循著各時令的產物來製作季節性食品。因此要尋覓各個作物合適的耕作地，如在冷的地方種植芋頭、番薯、南瓜、玉米、豆類、疏菜、紅藜等；在暖的地方種植小米、高粱、樹豆、豆子、花生、芒果、香蕉、檳榔、山藥及其他作物。作物收成後，可烘乾芋頭，作為芋頭乾；亦或是製作小米糕餅。有好多的想法，在糧食缺少的條件下，卻能發展出多用途的料理智慧。",
      "ab": "Kay Ngudradrekay malrigiliringa pautaleke, tutaleke, ngitaleke, pangitaleke, makalra turamuru ku tapangimiamiane kudra ki akaneane lini ikay tavanane, ikay ki cekele niiyane ka muakalrivili ki lakacalrisiane. Singiakay ki kalamanemanane pikay ku satuakaneanane ku nikitalekane, lakisamula ngudalrane silape ku tapautalekane ini, pikay talidrekay pautai, pauvurasi, paugulrugulrane, paulapanay, paulepelepe, paulacenge, paubae; \r\n[===]\r\npikay talilabelabe pautaleke ku becenge, paurumagay, paukaridrange, paulepelepe, paumakapairange, paukamadha, paubelebele, pausabiki, pautuba si drumane ka taleke. Latukuray ku tai pikay ki takutuane, tuabay ku becenge, thathatha ku tapangimiane ku amudruane ku taleke.",
      "order": "1",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2020/12/27/849e8eb895308e298f803b71ac4de06a.wav",
